cff-version:  2.0.3
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "jstage-mcp: An MCP server for the J-STAGE WebAPI"
abstract: >-
  A FastMCP stdio server that exposes the J-STAGE WebAPI (Japan Science and
  Technology Agency) as four tools for AI clients: article search, journal
  issue listing, journal search, and DOI lookup. Returns bilingual
  (English/Japanese) metadata and includes JST attribution in every response.
